metadata.name: Romantic Retro #1/20
metadata.description:
Romantic Retro //  
As an enthusiast of Retro setups and retro images, I wanted to show my creativity about it. So, I created a retro inspired artwork with creative lighting, and one of my favorite game Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas in screen.  
Artwork info:  
Dimensions: 4000 by 5000 pixels  
Print Friendly: Yes
